G |- a : [x:A] -> B 
G Rel |- b : A
--------------------------- ::  eapp
G |- a [b] : B [ b / x ]


G |- A : Type     
G, x:Rel A |- B : Type
-------------------------------------- :: epi
G |- [x:A] -> B : Type


